DTC P0703: Brake Switch “B” Circuit
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Brake light switch signal is not received during 1 D/C even if driving at specified speed and for specified time.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(2 D/C detection logic for type A)
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(2 D/C detection logic but transmission warning light does not light up for type B and C)
</ptxt>
</entry>
